## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture the full spectrum of beliefs within Christianity. Additionally, interpretations of religious texts are inherently subjective and can vary significantly among individuals and denominations. The report focuses on English-language sources, which may not reflect global perspectives on the issue.

